filter.inkscape:menu-tooltip: Overlays two copies with different blur amounts and modifiable blend and composite

text.tspan: - use this area to test logo against various background
- before export, check that every text (of the selection to export) are converted into path, reader may not have the font available on its system
- select group/object to export, export only the selection as "plain SVG" into the target destination
- scale width to be the same width as logo above
- scale height to be like other
- select a text's color, use HSLA, set L=48
- set stroke color of circle to text's color with L=60
- set gradiant color of logo from text's color to same color with L=73
- group every objects, label the group and set id (via properties) to the same name, id will be used as default value for export
- convert every object into path the merge them
